issue.title: TF to Torch Migrate Combiner Part4b
issue.body:
# Code Pull Requests

Part of Issue #1324.

Summary of changes:
* Port `TabTransformerCombiner` to Torch
* updated unit test for `TabTransformerCombiner` 
* clean up `forward()` calls to remove TF specific parameters from all combiners
* Add typing hints 

Work-in-Progress

body: TabNet Combiner to be submitted under a new PR.
